      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">論語 15.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Analects III.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「由，知德者鮮矣！」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "Yu, those who know virtue are few."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="lunyu__book-15-weilinggong__004__zhwikisource-20260529__legge-cc-v1-1893">
