      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">論語 15.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Analects IV.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「無爲而治者，其舜也與！夫何爲哉？恭己正南面而已矣。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "May not Shun be instanced as having governed efficiently without exertion? What did he do? He did nothing but gravely and reverently occupy his royal seat."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="lunyu__book-15-weilinggong__005__zhwikisource-20260529__legge-cc-v1-1893">
