      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">論語 15.8</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Analects VIII.8</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「志士仁人，無求生以害仁，有殺身以成仁。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "The determined scholar and the man of virtue will not seek to live at the expense of injuring their virtue. They will even sacrifice their lives to preserve their virtue complete."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="lunyu__book-15-weilinggong__009__zhwikisource-20260529__legge-cc-v1-1893">
