      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「人無遠慮，必有近憂。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "If a man take no thought about what is distant, he will find sorrow near at hand."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="lunyu__book-15-weilinggong__012__zhwikisource-20260529__legge-cc-v1-1893">
