      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「已矣乎！吾未見好德如好色者也！」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "It is all over! I have not seen one who loves virtue as he loves beauty."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
