      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「臧文仲，其竊位者與！知柳下惠之賢，而不與立也。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "Was not Tsang Wan like one who had stolen his situation? He knew the virtue and the talents of Hui of Liu-hsia, and yet did not procure that he should stand with him in court."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
