      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「君子義以爲質，禮以行之，孫以出之，信以成之。君子哉！」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "The superior man in everything considers righteousness to be essential. He performs it according to the rules of propriety. He brings it forth in humility. He completes it with sincerity. This is indeed a superior man."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
