      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子貢問曰：「有一言而可以終身行之者乎？」子曰：「其恕乎！己所不欲，勿施於人。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Tsze-kung asked, saying, "Is there one word which may serve as a rule of practice for all one's life?" The Master said, "Is not reciprocity such a word? What you do not want done to yourself, do not do to others."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="lunyu__book-15-weilinggong__024__zhwikisource-20260529__legge-cc-v1-1893">
