      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「吾猶及史之闕文也，有馬者，借人乘之。今亡矣夫！」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "Even in my early days, a historiographer would leave a blank in his text, and he who had a horse would lend him to another to ride. Now, alas! there are no such things."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
