      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "I have been the whole day without eating, and the whole night without sleeping:—occupied with thinking. It was of no use. The better plan is to learn."</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="lunyu__book-15-weilinggong__031__zhwikisource-20260529__legge-cc-v1-1893">
