      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">論語 15.37</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Analects XXXVII.37</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>子曰：「事君，敬其事而後其食。」</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The Master said, "A minister, in serving his prince, reverently discharges his duties, and makes his emolument a secondary consideration."</seg>
      </tuv>
